{"id": "lunchcultuur-in-de-lage-landen-kansen-voor-bourgondische-lunchrevolutie__a2-late-chunking__0015", "text": "The Leisure sector has largely gone through a difficult period. The recovery has started with the phasing out of the measures regarding corona. The terraces are starting to fill up, the number of tourists is increasing and events can be organized again. Staff shortages are now the biggest challenge. Digitizing staff work and spreading guests can limit the impact.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "lunchcultuur-in-de-lage-landen-kansen-voor-bourgondische-lunchrevolutie__a2-late-chunking__0015", "source_slug": "lunchcultuur-in-de-lage-landen-kansen-voor-bourgondische-lunchrevolutie", "source_title": "Lunch culture in the Low Countries: opportunities for a Burgundian lunch revolution", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/sectoren-en-trends/leisure/lunchcultuur-in-de-lage-landen-kansen-voor-bourgondische-lunchrevolutie.html", "source_date": "2025-06-13", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "leisure", "topic": "sectoren en trends", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 15, "n_chunks_total": 20, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 15}}
